ok chefs...here is a reciepe of Poha

1) Take poha(according to your hunger) and wash them by putting in a bowl and puring water. Finally filter out poha.
2)On a seprate pan(or kadahi) pour some oil, jeera and rai. Heat them until you listen cracking sound.
3) Then add mixture of cutted tomatoes,onion,mirchi,dhaniya in pan & fry them.
4) Add poha in pan & mix it.
5) Finally add haldi,sugar(acc to taste) in pan & mix it.
6) You can also add jaljira to make it more spicy.
7) Your are done :) 
